    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition. The exterior paint and body are flawless, with no scratches or dents. The interior is in like-new condition with no signs of wear. All mechanical and electronic systems are fully functional and operate as intended.",
