    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ideal for a buyer seeking a reliable mode of transportation without the premium price of a showroom-ready car. While the mechanical components are sound and the car runs well, there are noticeable cosmetic issues, including some paint oxidation on the roof and minor interior wear on the driver's seat. It has been regularly maintained, but expect the typical scuffs and scratches associated with a well-used daily driver. Sold as-is, it remains a solid, dependable choice for everyday use.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
