    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to pass this beauty along to a new home. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve treated it like royalty\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single week. You won't find a single blemish on it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for perfection, this is it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 43500.0,
