    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the legendary S54 platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power through its six individual throttle bodies, with the double-VANOS system operating flawlessly. The Getrag 6-speed manual offers crisp, precise gates, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. This vehicle features a reinforced rear subframe and a pristine undercarriage, free of oxidation. The original paint retains its deep luster, and the interior demonstrates zero bolster wear or pixel degradation in the instrument cluster. Mechanically sound with documented valve adjustments and rod bearing service, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning collector.",
